OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudier but dry start in the
OL,6,Feast, with the odd spot of rain
OL,7,Fpossible through the morning. Turning
OL,8,Fbrighter later with a very isolated
OL,9,Fshower possible. Feeling much cooler
OL,10,Fthen recent days with near normal
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry end to the afternoon
OL,14,Fwith clear spells developing. Turning
OL,15,Fcloudier later in the night with an
OL,16,Fincreasing risk of patchy drizzle
OL,17,Facross the hills and moors by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
