OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA largely cloudy morning on
OL,6,FFriday with outbreaks of rain pushing
OL,7,Facross the region during the day.
OL,8,FStrengthening winds, these becoming
OL,9,Fgusty overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FUnsettled through the weekend and
OL,13,FMonday with sunny spells and showers
OL,14,For longer spells of rain. The showers
OL,15,Flocally heavy with thunder. Windy with
OL,16,Fcoastal gales possible, temperatures
OL,17,Fnear average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
